The Kapotah Cross Platform LAN Messaging and File Transfer Application

Shantanu Tushar http://www.shantanutushar.com
Sudhendu Kumar  http://www.sudhendu.in

1. INSTALL
You will need cmake and a C++ compiler with Qt libraries installed.
Download a Qt SDK from http://qt.nokia.com or install from your package manager.

cd kapotah
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
./Kapotah UserName

where UserName is the name you want to show on the network.
